wo-year hiatus from the sport she once dominated.\", \"from\": 240, \"to\": 402, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the twisties' Biles\", \"from\": 256, \"to\": 275}, {\"ngram\": \"several events\", \"from\": 304, \"to\": 318}, {\"ngram\": \"a two-year hiatus\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 367}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 373, \"to\": 382}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for latest news on the Paris Olympics Biles is far from alone in having faced a phenomena that is best described as a mental block that impact the spatial awareness of gymnasts.\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 613, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 434}, {\"ngram\": \"latest news\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 450}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics Biles\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"a phenomena\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 524}, {\"ngram\": \"a mental block\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 565}, {\"ngram\": \"the spatial awareness\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 599}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnasts\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 611}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old was particularly badly affected by the twisties during the vault competition during which her timing was well off as she struggled to nail her routine.\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 782, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the twisties\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 678}, {\"ngram\": \"the vault competition\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 707}, {\"ngram\": \"her timing\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 731}, {\"ngram\": \"her routine\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked to explain the twisties, Biles' teammate Laurie Hernandez explained: 'The rhythm is off, and your brain will like stutter step for half a second and that's enough to throw off the whole skill.\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 831, \"end\": 847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\