ence\": \"I worked a lot on myself and I believe in myself a little bit more, just coming back out here and starting the first steps again.\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"the first steps\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1678}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It means the world because after everything that kind of transpired in Tokyo and it took a lot.\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1783, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1759, \"end\": 1764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9963964480480383, \"rank\": 0.0036165590529644693, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1706}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I worked on myself a lot, I still do therapy weekly and it's just been so exciting to come out here and have the confidence I had before.'\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1924, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"therapy\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1830}, {\"ngram\": \"the confidence\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1909}]}, {\"sentence\": \"28 July - Team Qualifying: Simone Biles is making her first appearance in the team qualifying events.\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 2027, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"28 July - Team Qualifying\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 1951}, {\"ngram\": \"Simone Biles\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1965}, {\"ngram\": \"her first appearance\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 1996}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2008}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2026}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She will feature alongside her USA teammates (Jordan Chiles, Hezly Rivera and Sunisa Lee) in Subdivision 2 from 10:40am BST (11:40am CET